{"tid":1807621,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[2020 - 2023] 第六屆觀塘區區議會監察討論區 I","createTime":"2020-01-02T02:19:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-17T03:00:58.000Z","uid":32934,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"7b419491013c7fb736305fbb08493771e7cf2271","tid":1807621,"uid":32934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T02:19:56.000Z","msg":"第六屆區議會正式走馬上任<br />\n選左出黎，唔係就咁就算<br />\n我地有責任監察議會，幫助各區新任議員<br />\n同時提醒佢地小心誘惑<br />\n<br />\n呢個大家可以討論返佢地既會議<br />\n或者區內有咩問題可以拎出黎講<br />\n一齊改善區內問題<br />\n我諗佢地都識睇連登，都會睇到既<br />\n<br />\n不過我諗首要問題係睇下點處理5千萬噴泉<br />\n<br />\n喺度祝各觀塘區區議員工作順利、一帆風順！"},{"pid":"eea938f28b8be120291f7bc871bda50df9fe60fe","tid":1807621,"uid":122205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T02:29:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f27ad80c3acbf3db319be2040533a4f7d946b07","tid":1807621,"uid":32934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T02:30:56.000Z","msg":"區議員名單︰<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.districtcouncils.gov.hk/kt/tc_chi/members/info/dc_member_list.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.districtcouncils.gov.hk%2Fkt%2Ftc_chi%2Fmembers%2Finfo%2Fdc_member_list.php&d=navV%2BA4%2FMRIetR8KyPOOAJLurRSHZiEGX9rhKonVocs%3D&h=9f06353f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.districtcouncils.gov.hk/kt/tc_chi/members/info/dc_member_list.php</a><br />\n<br />\n第一次區議會大會<br />\n2020-01-07 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.districtcouncils.gov.hk/kt/tc_chi/meetings/dcmeetings/dc_meetings.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.districtcouncils.gov.hk%2Fkt%2Ftc_chi%2Fmeetings%2Fdcmeetings%2Fdc_meetings.php&d=navV%2BA4%2FMRIetR8KyPOOAJLurRSHZiEGX9rhKonVocs%3D&h=ba1e28b8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.districtcouncils.gov.hk/kt/tc_chi/meetings/dcmeetings/dc_meetings.php</a>"},{"pid":"4a60448eec67782f317972bd6758b587415f70e3","tid":1807621,"uid":325516,"like":0,"dis